title: Made $250,000+ TAX FREE Selling a Rental Property #shorts
text: I just made a quarter million dollars tax-free selling a house that I haven't lived in for two years. This is exactly why I talk about investing in multiple mediums. For me, it's the stock market real estate in angel investing. By doing this, it allows me to identify opportunity, rotate capital to where I can take advantage of the opportunity, and do it all over again. So if you're interested in learning more about my approach to developing wealth, subscribe to the account, share with some friends, and I'll catch you all later, be an outlier.
